<p>I knew LEAF was about to start with his bird. Don&rsquo;t ask me how &ndash; it&rsquo;s a trade secret.
Part of what makes me the incredible trainer I am. I remembered watching the first episode
of the anime and how quickly all those sparrows got fried from Ash&rsquo;s Pikachu<img src="https://img.pokemondb.net/sprites/firered-leafgreen/normal/pikachu.png"
     alt="Pikachu"
     style="height:48px; vertical-align:middle; margin: -0.5rem">
.</p>
<p>I knew exactly who to use. &ldquo;GO PIKABLUE<img src="https://img.pokemondb.net/sprites/firered-leafgreen/normal/pikachu.png"
